name: Squibbly Sqwob's Big Day Out
overview: A smash TV style arena shooter with charming cartoony graphics. Welcome to cutesy land, you are the famous (well almost famous) cartoon character "Squibbly Sqwob". But all is not well in the cutesy land as the evil ink blot has stolen all the ink pens so no one can draw any cartoons, so you must get back the pens and kill ink blot. Good Luck.
